back from battle. Foxfingers said with an innocent charm in his 
voice. "Oh how rude of me, I'm Foxfingers, maximal imnfiltration and 
retrieval specialist." 

A nicer term for a thief couldn't have been tmought of by anyone who 
wasn't one. Grimmlers new aquaintance extended his hand toward 
Grimmler. "It's a pleasure to finally be reunited with a maximal 
group."
